./sdp/logs/Lead_frac-0113_1777794485.log:4324:my-claw/sdp/prd-cypherclaw-sampler.md:91:| CCS-003 | Implement `SampleLibrary` on-disk store backed by `index.sqlite` with tag/source/pitch/mood-range queries. | MUST | T1 | - `SampleLibrary(root: Path)` opens / creates `index.sqlite` with table `samples` carrying every `SampleRecord` field plus full-text-search index on `character_tags`<br/>- `library.add(record)` persists row + verifies file presence<br/>- `library.find(source=, character_any=, character_all=, pitch_band=, arc_phase=, mood_range=, limit=)` returns ordered list (most recent first within match set)<br/>- tests cover insert, query by each filter, empty-result path, and corrupted-DB rebuild |
./sdp/logs/Lead_frac-0113_1777794485.log:4325:my-claw/sdp/prd-cypherclaw-sampler.md:96:| CCS-008 | Register `voice_sampler` character in `character_registry.py` with `voice.synth = "sw_sampler"`, `voice.role = "sampler"`, default register, and per-mode gain overrides. | MUST | T1 | - `character_registry.py` gains `voice_sampler` entry with synth=`sw_sampler`, role=`sampler`, register=`[36, 84]`, params containing default grain_size_ms, density, pitch_transpose<br/>- character is selectable by `select_cast_ids` when `preferred_synths` includes `sw_sampler`<br/>- tests verify registration and selection through cast planner |
./sdp/logs/Lead_frac-0113_1777794485.log:4326:my-claw/sdp/prd-cypherclaw-sampler.md:97:| CCS-009 | Implement `sw_sampler.scd` granular SynthDef with bufnum, grain-size, density, position-scrub, pitch-transpose, attack/release envelope, and effects-bus send. | MUST | T1 | - SynthDef args: `bufnum`, `amp` (default 0.5), `grain_size_ms` (default 80, range 20–200), `density` (default 12 grains/sec), `position` (0..1 normalized), `position_rate` (scrub speed), `pitch_transpose_semitones` (default 0), `pitch_jitter_semitones` (default 0.1), `attack_sec` (default 0.05), `release_sec` (default 0.2), `gate` (default 1, sustained), `out_bus` (default 0), `fx_send` (default 0.4)<br/>- `doneAction:2` self-frees on envelope end<br/>- compiled `sw_sampler.scsyndef` lives in `synthesis/synthdefs/`<br/>- SC-side test (`my-claw/supercollider/test_sw_sampler.scd`) renders 2-second clip from a known buffer and verifies non-silence + spectral characteristics<br/>- gate=0 triggers release tail correctly |
./sdp/logs/Lead_frac-0113_1777794485.log:4327:my-claw/sdp/prd-cypherclaw-sampler.md:99:| CCS-011 | Implement `sampler_effects.scd` dedicated effects-bus SynthDef chain: long delay (1/4 to 1/2 measure), convolution reverb (FreeVerb fallback if no IR loaded), spectral freeze (PV_Freeze), comb-resonance tuned to B fundamental (61.74 Hz). | MUST | T1 | - SynthDef `sw_sampler_fx` reads from a stereo bus and writes to master bus<br/>- args: `delay_time` (sec, default 0.5), `delay_feedback` (0..0.85, default 0.55), `verb_mix` (default 0.35), `room_size` (default 0.7), `freeze_amount` (0..1, default 0.0), `comb_b_amount` (0..1, default 0.25), `comb_b_freq` (default 61.74)<br/>- bus number conventionally 16 (stereo, so 16+17)<br/>- compiled `sw_sampler_fx.scsyndef` lives in `synthesis/synthdefs/`<br/>- SC-side test verifies non-silent output for a known impulse input and frequency-domain check that 61.74 Hz comb peak is present when `comb_b_amount > 0` |
./sdp/logs/Lead_frac-0113_1777794485.log:4328:my-claw/sdp/prd-cypherclaw-sampler.md:100:| CCS-012 | Implement `sampler_dispatch.py` that converts a `(SampleRecord, PerformanceIntent, params)` tuple into the OSC bundle (`/s_new sw_sampler ...` + buffer-pool acquire) and ships it to scsynth. | MUST | T1 | - `dispatch_sample(record, intent, *, position, position_rate, grain_size_ms, density, pitch_transpose, amp, fx_send) -> SamplerHandle` issues `/b_allocRead` (if needed), `/s_new sw_sampler ...` and returns a handle for later `/n_set gate 0` release<br/>- correlates `record.gain_db` with `amp`<br/>- handles per-mode effects presets (delay_time / verb_mix / freeze / comb_b vary by mode)<br/>- tests with mock OSC client verify correct bundle ordering, gate-release path, and per-mode preset application |
./sdp/logs/Lead_frac-0113_1777794485.log:4329:my-claw/sdp/prd-cypherclaw-sampler.md:101:| CCS-013 | Per-voice gate-controlled lifecycle: composer can `play_sampler(record, duration_sec)` for fire-and-forget OR `start_sampler(record) -> handle; stop_sampler(handle)` for sustained voices. | MUST | T1 | - `sampler_dispatch.play_sampler(record, duration_sec, **params)` schedules a fire-and-forget grain cloud with an internal envelope of `duration_sec`<br/>- `start_sampler` / `stop_sampler` returns/uses a handle for sustained sampler voices that match the bowed/pad lifecycle<br/>- both code paths feed through the same `dispatch_sample` core<br/>- tests verify both lifecycles and that they can run concurrently without buffer-id collision |
./sdp/logs/Lead_frac-0113_1777794485.log:4330:my-claw/sdp/prd-cypherclaw-sampler.md:102:| CCS-014 | Integrate sampler effects bus into `master_bus.py` mix slot with appropriate gain staging (peak-normalized, not RMS) and post-mix compression bypass to preserve grain transients. | MUST | T1 | - `master_bus.apply_master_bus_scene` recognizes a `sampler_bus` mix slot with default gain -3 dB (peak-normalized so quieter library samples don't disappear)<br/>- post-mix compression for the sampler slot has `compression_ratio = 1.5` (lower than the 4.0 used elsewhere) so grain transients survive<br/>- tests verify gain staging on a known-amplitude input and grain-transient preservation via peak-vs-RMS ratio |
./sdp/logs/Lead_frac-0113_1777794485.log:4331:my-claw/sdp/prd-cypherclaw-sampler.md:114:| CCS-026 | Add per-mode effects-bus presets: solitary/evening favor more reverb + delay; working_ambience uses minimal effects; storm uses high freeze + heavy comb-B. | MUST | T1 | - `sampler_dispatch::FX_PRESETS_BY_MODE: dict[str, dict]` mapping mode name to fx args<br/>- solitary: `delay_time=0.6, delay_feedback=0.65, verb_mix=0.45, freeze_amount=0.2, comb_b_amount=0.4`<br/>- companion: `delay_time=0.5, delay_feedback=0.4, verb_mix=0.3, freeze_amount=0.0, comb_b_amount=0.15`<br/>- working_ambience: `delay_time=0.3, delay_feedback=0.2, verb_mix=0.15, freeze_amount=0.0, comb_b_amount=0.1`<br/>- evening_reflection: `delay_time=0.7, delay_feedback=0.55, verb_mix=0.5, freeze_amount=0.15, comb_b_amount=0.3`<br/>- storm: `delay_time=0.25, delay_feedback=0.7, verb_mix=0.25, freeze_amount=0.55, comb_b_amount=0.6`<br/>- tests verify each preset, that values are within SynthDef-acceptable ranges, and that `dispatch_sample` correctly applies the preset for the active mode |
