+   - **VERIFY:** `rg -n "T-054d|sub-second fan-out|vitest-pool-workers|New Worker dev dependencies|No D1 database migration|No Durable Object migration|startup identity" CHANGELOG.md progress.md ESCALATIONS.md specs/t-054d-spec.md`
